Go ahead. Try it!

1403
01:23:41,534 --> 01:23:43,940
- No!
- Eh?

1404
01:23:44,281 --> 01:23:47,470
I hate being dead!
This sucks!

1405
01:23:47,570 --> 01:23:50,937
I hate it more than life!
I hate the way you are!

1406
01:23:51,037 --> 01:23:52,633
I hate you!

1407
01:23:52,733 --> 01:23:54,726
It's stupid how we're
in this limo!

1408
01:23:54,826 --> 01:23:57,411
It's stupid, that thing
you're doing with your ear!

1409
01:23:57,511 --> 01:24:00,962
That rule about
18,000 times is lame!

1410
01:24:01,062 --> 01:24:02,698
I don't like it here at all!

1411
01:24:02,798 --> 01:24:05,548
There's no tunnel!
The least you could have done

1412
01:24:05,648 --> 01:24:07,493
was giving me a tunnel
with a bright light!

1413
01:24:07,593 --> 01:24:11,144
Nobody has ever come back
and said: "Oh, it was so peaceful;

1414
01:24:11,244 --> 01:24:13,566
I was in this big
stretch limo."

1415
01:24:13,666 --> 01:24:15,563
Oh, th--this is great!

1416
01:24:15,914 --> 01:24:18,193
I'm not even floating!
You know?

1417
01:24:18,293 --> 01:24:20,511
You'd at least think
I'd be floating or something.

1418
01:24:20,611 --> 01:24:22,848
No, no, no!
I'm in the back of a car,

1419
01:24:22,948 --> 01:24:25,390
with a guy that can
relocate his ear!

1420
01:24:25,490 --> 01:24:29,715
Oh, this must be Heaven!
Somebody pinch me!

1421
01:24:31,418 --> 01:24:34,505
And look at you.

1422
01:24:34,605 --> 01:24:39,063
Yeah, you with your face
popping up all over the place.

1423
01:24:39,163 --> 01:24:42,461
Yeah, maybe all I did was complain.
Maybe I didn't help anyone.

1424
01:24:42,561 --> 01:24:44,181
But at least I wasn't
just showing up,

1425
01:24:44,281 --> 01:24:47,011
trying to scare people
24 hours a day!

1426
01:24:47,111 --> 01:24:49,645
Oh, there's a lot of things
that need to be changed around here!

1427
01:24:49,745 --> 01:24:51,329
And as soon
as I see a little bit more,

1428
01:24:51,429 --> 01:24:54,689
I'm gonna give you a full,
detailed rundown

1429
01:24:54,789 --> 01:24:58,528
of the way things should be!
And you're gonna hear it, man!

1430
01:24:58,628 --> 01:25:00,973
You're gonna hear it all!

1431
01:25:01,320 --> 01:25:03,616
Not this time, pal!

1432
01:25:03,716 --> 01:25:06,555
First, when people think
about death and dying,

1433
01:25:06,655 --> 01:25:10,475
they're building up expectations.

1434
01:25:10,575 --> 01:25:15,324
And it is your responsibility
to make sure they're not let down.

1435
01:25:15,424 --> 01:25:17,932
And whoa!
Believe me!

1436
01:25:18,032 --> 01:25:22,500
This is one, gigantic let-down!

1437
01:25:22,839 --> 01:25:24,596
For instance, when you die,

1438
01:25:24,696 --> 01:25:28,171
did you ever think maybe you'd like
to see someone that you like?

1439
01:25:28,271 --> 01:25:30,490
You know,
like a relative or something?

1440
01:25:30,590 --> 01:25:33,870
Not some rubber-faced
limbo champion!

1441
01:25:33,970 --> 01:25:37,854
Oh yeah, I'm dead now.
Please bring in Mr. Play-Doh Face.

1442
01:25:37,954 --> 01:25:41,859
That would be nice!
I'd like to be annoyed for eternity!

1443
01:25:41,959 --> 01:25:45,599
Bring me the loser!
Yeah, I love being around him!

1444
01:25:45,699 --> 01:25:47,515
It's great!

1445
01:25:48,325 --> 01:25:49,380
Thane?

1446
01:25:49,480 --> 01:25:51,775
Hey, Thane!
Thane?

1447
01:25:53,380 --> 01:25:56,074
Hey... God, Tha--
Thane!

1448
01:25:57,183 --> 01:25:58,442
I can't believe this.

1449
01:25:59,052 --> 01:26:01,060
I gotta call the police.
Hey!

1450
01:26:03,683 --> 01:26:05,139
You're alive?

1451
01:26:07,028 --> 01:26:09,554
- Yeah?
- You were dead!

1452
01:26:11,157 --> 01:26:12,263
Was I?

1453
01:26:12,363 --> 01:26:14,162
You were laying right there.
You had no pulse.

1454
01:26:15,974 --> 01:26:17,115
Really?

1455
01:26:17,894 --> 01:26:19,339
What happened?

1456
01:26:19,718 --> 01:26:21,628
Do you remember anything?

1457
01:26:23,062 --> 01:26:24,491
This limo.

1458
01:26:24,926 --> 01:26:28,803
And there was this guy
that took his ear off.

1459
01:26:31,733 --> 01:26:34,971
I'm hungry.
Let's get something to eat.

1460
01:26:35,285 --> 01:26:37,374
Wait, wait, wait.
Y-you feel up to that?

1461
01:26:37,474 --> 01:26:39,397
I mean... are you okay?

1462
01:26:40,301 --> 01:26:42,283
I feel great!

1463
01:26:43,310 --> 01:26:46,593
- Come on, let's go.
- You mean go out?

1464
01:26:46,693 --> 01:26:49,050
And get something to eat
at a restaurant?

1465
01:26:49,150 --> 01:26:51,101
Yeah, what's the problem?

1466
01:26:51,201 --> 01:26:55,150
Hey, Thane, let me get this straight.
You wanna go to a restaurant?

1467
01:26:55,250 --> 01:26:57,664
Yeah, but I'm telling you, man,
they better have cereal.

1468
01:26:57,764 --> 01:27:01,383
And none of this: "Oh, we only
serve it in the morning."

1469
01:29:13,014 --> 01:29:14,442
I'm sorry.

1470
01:29:14,646 --> 01:29:16,675
This time I'm gonna
have to put my foot down.

1471
01:29:16,775 --> 01:29:18,001
I'm not taking him.

1472
01:29:18,101 --> 01:29:20,589
There's no way I can
be around that guy.

1473
01:29:21,325 --> 01:29:23,701
And I'm not coming back
for him, either.

